<Link id="l00801" /><CodeLine lineNumber="801"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// Have a map, with key being the matching prefix length, and the value</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00802" /><CodeLine lineNumber="802"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// being the list of pairs (R,S), where R&#39;s prefix matches VR at S.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00803" /><CodeLine lineNumber="803"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// (DenseMap&lt;uint16&#95;t,RSListType&gt; fails to instantiate.)</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l01200" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1200"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// Second, compare &quot;averages&quot;, i.e. use-count per size. The lower wins.</span></CodeLine>
